          .hoof-info-left
            .hoof-intro-copy
              %h1 drink well.
              %p Our take on what a cocktail bar should be. Classic and modern libations, addictive bar snacks and a beautiful environment. We also have a nice wine and beer list, but you should probably have a cocktail.
            %h2 come drink.
            %address
              923 Dundas Street West
              %br
              Toronto ON M6J 1W3
            %p
              No reservastions, sorry! For other inquires,&nbsp;
              %a{href: "mailto:hoofcocktailbar@gmail.com", title: "Make a Reservation"} email us!
              &nbsp;We'd also like to remind everyone to bring a mask!
            %a{href: "#map", class: "btn"} Map
          .hoof-info-right
            %h2 cocktail hours
            %table.hoof-info-hours



